title: Did Vince Foster shoot himself "three times in the back of the head" to avoid testifying against Hillary Clinton?
subtitle: An old conspiracy theory about Clinton's 1993 suicide (Vincent Foster), whose death was investigated by Supreme Court candidate Brett Cavanaugh, was again examined in September 2018.
author: David Emery
vclaim: "Clinton's assistant Vince Foster shot himself three times in the back of his head to avoid testifying against Hillary Clinton."
